column2: select z.specobjid, dbo.fPhotoFlagsN(p.flags), p.ra, p.dec, p.flags into mydb.dis_test from PhotoObj p   join zoo2MainSpecz z on p.specobjid=z.specobjid where   z.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_disturbed_debiased > z.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_irregular_debiased   and   z.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_disturbed_debiased > #   and    z.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_disturbed_flag <> #   and   (p.flags & dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) = #
